metadata.name: CandyLand
metadata.description:
Candy skies or just a beautiful sunset, where I live in Perth theyâ€™re a common occurrence.

I love capturing ocean reflections, you only have a few milliseconds to decide when to click the shutter, stall and you will miss the scene.

This really is a true 1/1 image, the clouds in the sky and the patterns in the sand will never be repeated in this way again.

This is Marmion Marine Park in Perth, Western Australia.
